Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite place for bowling fun. My name is Emily. How can I assist you today?

Hi Emily, I have a question about my recent billing.

Of course! I’m happy to help. Could I please start by asking for your name?

Sure, it’s Jack Thompson.

Thank you, Jack. To pull up your billing information, could you please provide me with your account number?

Yes, it’s A one two three four five six B.

Great, thank you. I just need to verify your registered zip code as well, please.

It’s zero two six six eight.

Perfect, thank you for that information. I have your account details now. What specific billing issue can I help you with?

I noticed an unexpected charge on my last statement and wanted to understand what it’s for.

I’ll be happy to look into that for you. Please hold on for a moment while I check your last billing statement.

Alright, thank you.

Thank you for waiting, Jack. I see there was a charge on October fifth for shoe rental during our weekend tournament. Does that sound correct?

Oh yes, I forgot about that tournament. That makes sense. Thanks for clarifying!

You’re welcome! If you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time, Jack, and enjoy your day!

Thanks, Emily. You too!
